data.description:
This lovely single-family home located in Belgrade, MT offers 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, with a fully finished basement that provides additional living space.
The main floor features a living room, dining room, and kitchen. The kitchen includes ample cabinetry, modern appliances and opens to the dining room and living room, creating a great space for entertaining. There are 2 nicely-sized bedrooms on the main floor, along with a full bathroom. Downstairs you'll find a spacious finished basement with a large rec room, 1 additional bedroom, and a full bathroom. The basement offers room to grow - it can easily be converted into a 4th bedroom if desired.
The home sits on a nice lot with mature trees, a fully-fenced backyard, and a deck, perfect for hosting barbeques and gatherings. Located in a quiet Belgrade neighborhood, it provides easy access to downtown amenities, restaurants, schools, and more. Schedule your showing today!
